A secure, sharded backend tool collects parachain data every 6 seconds, computing metrics with 99% reliability (0.005 DOT per update), tested on Rococo vs. Ethereumâ€™s 2024 systems ($4B daily volume). It supports 50+ parachains, adjusting VTS weights dynamically (e.g., 0.25 for PoV if RWAI <0.30, reverting to 0.20 each at $10,000,000 RWAI TVL). The Transparency Portal stores audit reports and vote history on IPFS (0.001 DOT per hash), ensuring openness. Non-technical voters may need guides to understand its role.

Technical: Sharded computation ensures scalability. Audits (3,000 DOT) verify logic. Gas costs align with Polkadotâ€™s 2024 benchmarks (0.005 DOT per transaction).

