3.7 VTS and VMAI

Voxonomics Trust Score (VTS) and VOXD Macroeconomic Alignment Index (VMAI) anchor VOXDâ€™s stability and Polkadotâ€™s global trust, displayed on VOXUIâ€™s â€œMacro Tabâ€ with clear visuals and scenario toggles, empowering voters to assess economic health.

