VTS (0.85) averages five metricsâ€”PoV (0.85), OPI (0.80), DLI (0.78), PTI (0.85), RWAI (0.25)â€”with dynamic weights (e.g., 0.25 for PoV if RWAI <0.30, else 0.20 each at $10,000,000 RWAI TVL). VTS drives VOXDâ€™s peg and VOX Forex Market trading (e.g., VOXD/VOXA = 1.18 for VTS 0.85/0.72). VOXUIâ€™s â€œMetrics Tabâ€ shows VTS as a glowing gauge with a â€œHigh Trustâ€ badge, clear as a health monitor.

Technical: VTS updates hourly (0.005 DOT cost), sourced from Polkadot.js (votes), Subscan (transactions), and HydraDX (liquidity). Audits (3,000 DOT) verify logic.

