5.7 Regulatory Resilience

A 12,000 DOT legal fund navigates MiCA, SEC, and MAS/DMCC rules, countering USDTâ€™s 2024 regulatory risks (30% ban probability). The â€œRegulatory Circuit Breakerâ€ ensures VOXDâ€™s continuity, unlike Terraâ€™s 2022 collapse.

